1. The Person class should have methods:
 sayHello(),
 celebrateEaster(),
 isAdult(),
 canTakeLoan()
    with the relevant parameters if any.
2. sayHello() should print Hello based on concrete person spoken language,
 default is in English.
3. celebrateEaster should print if the concrete person
 celebrates Easter based on their religion.
4. isAdult should take in consideration the country of residence.
5. canTakeLoan is based on the job.

